: "1921-02-04", "dates": ["1921-02-04"], "description": ["V \u00dcBSCRJPTION People who make the most noise generally have tlie least to say Good advice is seldom acceptable be cause its quality is not recognized Lenin the Russian dictator denies that lie is dead Possibly he knows Regardless of price conditions the crop of free advice has not diminished Hurrah for the fellow who says hurrah forthls town Are you guilt V Theres a master mind in eve r y home but sometimes it isnt spelled that way Its no trouble at all to speak a kind word Just think it and it will slip right out You can always tell when a fellow has reached his dotage He calls her his wonder girl We thank you are perfectly satis fied with lU2L Each day is quite as we expected it to be Senator Thomas is quite correct the bootlegginglftdustry probably is our most flourishing industry Charity invariably begins at home but in most cases there is not enough to go beyond the first person Yes William spring is ambling right along But it has no originality it does the same each year Mr Harding approaches the 4th of March in fear andtrembling He may forget the first line"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-06-25T23:45:57.427Z", "group": ["ndnp/sdhi", "south-dakota-state-historical-society-state-archives-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn96090217/1921-02-04/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:sdhi:batch_sdhi_carrot_ver02:data:sn96090217:00279522928:1921020401:1114/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=384&w=270", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:sdhi:batch_sdhi_carrot_ver02:data:sn96090217:00279522928:1921020401:1114/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=769&w=541", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/sdhi/batch_sdhi_carrot_ver02/data/sn96090217/00279522928/1921020401/1114.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["white river", "melle